cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV. 

The paper proposes a method for hyperparameter tuning in policy gradient methods, which are commonly used in machine learning for reinforcement learning tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also includes experiments on image-based tasks, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the use of trajectories and policy updates suggests a possible connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
